flowchart TD
    A[Agent (Claude Code / IDE Agent)] -->|Tool Call| H[Hook: PreToolUse]
    H --> G[MCP Context Server (Context Mode)]
    G -->|Run tool in sandboxed subprocess| T[Tool Execution (FS/Web/Shell)]
    T --> O[Raw Output]

    O -->|< threshold (e.g., 5KB)| S[Summarize]
    O -->|>= threshold| C[Chunk]
    C --> I[Index in SQLite FTS5 (BM25)]

    S --> R[Return short summary]
    I --> R2[Return: indexed confirmation + summary + handle]

    A <-- R
    A <-- R2

    A -->|Targeted query| Q[ctx_search / ctx_fetch]
    Q --> G
    G --> I
    I --> SNIP[Return matching snippets]
    A <-- SNIP

    %% Session continuity
    A --> E[Events: edits, git ops, tasks, errors, decisions]
    E --> DB[(SQLite event log)]

    A -->|Compaction triggered| PC[PreCompact Hook]
    PC --> G
    G --> SNAP[Build prioritized session snapshot (<~2KB)]
    A <-- SNAP
